# Purpose

Perform a structured final review for completed implementation work.

# Workflow

1. Use the `reviewer` custom agent to review the latest implementation.
2. Update `agent-workflow/artifacts/REVIEW.md`.
3. Prioritize correctness, regressions, plan compliance, and missing tests.

# Guardrails

- Do not edit application source files during review.
- Keep findings concrete and prioritized.
